imes.com/world/us-streamers/theburntpeanut-finally-reveals-fortnite-crossover-after-weeks-of-rumors/articleshow/131644101.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T01:22:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131644097,imgsize-1151623.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Video of Jesse Ridgway portraying character with Down syndrome resurfaces after announcement]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131644245.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[YouTuber Jesse Ridgway faces renewed scrutiny. An old video showing him portraying a character with Down syndrome has resurfaced. This comes after Ridgway announced he and his wife terminated a pregnancy after their unborn child was diagnosed with Trisomy 21. The resurfaced clip, from his series 'The Devil Inside', depicts exaggerated mannerisms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/video-of-jesse-ridgway-portraying-character-with-down-syndrome-resurfaces-after-announcement/articleshow/131644245.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/video-of-jesse-ridgway-portraying-character-with-down-syndrome-resurfaces-after-announcement/articleshow/131644245.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T02:11:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131644244,imgsize-641946.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump administration cracks down on ‘birth tourism’, revokes hundreds of visas]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131644173.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indi