ntion]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131641127.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Streamer Sneako sparked debate online after a viral reaction video showed him commenting on Kai Trump. In the clip, he called her “every Muslim’s dream girl” and said, “I pray she’s my wife.” Shared by Coinvo on X, the video drew mixed reactions, with some viewers finding it humorous while others criticized the comments and discussed the age difference.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-pray-shes-my-wife-sneako-shares-his-thoughts-on-kai-trump-as-viral-video-grabs-internet-attention/articleshow/131641127.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-pray-shes-my-wife-sneako-shares-his-thoughts-on-kai-trump-as-viral-video-grabs-internet-attention/articleshow/131641127.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-10T23:15:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131641048,imgsize-38884.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Elizabeth Fry: "Punishment is not for revenge, but to lessen..."]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131641162.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/quote-of-the-day-by-elizabeth-fry-punishment-is-not-for-revenge-but-to-lessen-/articleshow/131641162.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/quote-of-the-day-by-elizabeth-fry-punishment-is-not-for-revenge-but-to-lessen-/articleshow/131641162.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-10T23:08:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type